data.text:
I met up with Joe (Bomitoni) and his boyfriend and Douglas Park for a Cinco de Mayo festival. They had a series special guest: Eduardo Capetillo, Bibi Gaytan, Alex Sirvent and some other actress, who I cannot recall her name, but you could see her on the pictures. I got there late because I could not find a ride. Unfortunately, I was not able to take pictures with anyone but I took pictures of the celebrities on stage. I mostly took pictures of Eduardo because he was closer to the public and was the only one who kept facing and greeting his fans. I was surprised to see, what I assume, is a beer belly. Bibi is beautiful though and there is no way you can tell she had 4 kids and is in her mid 30's. Since there were a lot of people, I was not able to find Joe, until after the presentation. By the time I met up with Joe, he had already called Bibi's attention with the album he had of hers. He was fortunate to get an autograph and a picture, which I'm sure he'll post soon and I'll share. Bibi is absolutely gorgeous and a tad taller than her husband, Eduardo. Here are a few pictures:
